# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FITNESS BUDDY — Environment Configuration
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your credentials.
# NEVER commit the actual .env file to version control.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─── IBM Watsonx.ai Credentials (Required for AI features) ───────────────────
#
# Get these from: https://cloud.ibm.com/
# 1. Create an IBM Cloud account (Lite tier is free)
# 2. Create a Watsonx.ai project at https://dataplatform.cloud.ibm.com/
# 3. Get your API Key from: IBM Cloud → Manage → Access (IAM) → API Keys
# 4. Get your Project ID from: Watsonx.ai → Project → Manage → General
#

WATSONX_API_KEY=your_ibm_cloud_api_key_here
WATSONX_PROJECT_ID=your_watsonx_project_id_here
WATSONX_URL=https://au-syd.ml.cloud.ibm.com

# ─── IBM Granite Model Selection ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Available IBM Granite models on Watsonx.ai:
#   ibm/granite-13b-instruct-v2        (recommended, best for instructions)
#   ibm/granite-13b-chat-v2            (conversational)
#   ibm/granite-7b-lab                 (smaller, faster)
#   ibm/granite-3-8b-instruct          (Granite 3.x series)
#   ibm/granite-3-2b-instruct          (lightweight)

GRANITE_MODEL_ID=ibm/granite-13b-instruct-v2

# ─── Flask Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SECRET_KEY=change-this-to-a-strong-random-secret-key-in-production
FLASK_DEBUG=false
PORT=8080
